{"tid":866821,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"加國登台愛上大瀑布 黃心穎模仿力強","createTime":"2018-10-18T07:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T04:38:20.000Z","uid":160969,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc65d7ee5dcdf13a098b59006935cdd4910f8a4","tid":866821,"uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"黃心穎（Jacqueline）早前去咗加拿大蒙特利爾工作，寓工作於娛樂，又食又玩，不時在社交網上載靚相，留言：「我要活在藝術裏，montreal的街上到處都是壁畫。」對住鏡頭更不停擺甫士，牆壁上的人像哭，佢就扮喊，牆壁畫有隻眼珠，佢就睜大眼伸脷，模仿能力超強。<br />\n<br />\n不過，佢話最大開眼界就係睇尼亞加拉大瀑布，搞到佢日又睇，夜又睇，「今次去多倫多登台、住的fallsview casino resort 離 Niagara Falls 好近，發覺夜晚同日頭看瀑布的感覺完全不同。夜晚五光十色、影相會好靚，早上看就看到水流的衝力、好壯觀，但早上就要注意，好勁霧水、行得太近會成身濕晒，所以都要著雨衣。我希望下次可以試吓坐船，聽講都幾刺激，因為會好近瀑布，我相信到時一定會全身濕晒，建議夏天才坐。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2q6lhf7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2q6lhf7&d=0m12r7NV4xNHaDqtC9LzjMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f25d0268\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2q6lhf7</a>"},{"pid":"cf202e7101c62833c09418a02cffa79b1a9e67d0","tid":866821,"uid":17031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"成隻腳踩落人地幅塗鴉藝術到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f192a344763bcb1a4dbac4076460a4757f3c8b","tid":866821,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"搭高鐵北上啦<br />\n去乜撚加拿大啫"},{"pid":"52e9ac46b05d4184f6fa6a7765f0566891d3acf5","tid":866821,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"點解冇自信笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/161402_d5a5af2b1473e8bc21c66659342e9aba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F161402_d5a5af2b1473e8bc21c66659342e9aba.gif&h=c9b97caa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}